
These results are discussed in DREV memorandum, Aug/93.

Basically the result for default cases with the following circumstances:

We varied the amount of noise from 100 to 1000 by 100
10 test cases (different random seeds) for each of the noise values
Random variable instantiation ordering and constraint ordering

